    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to enjoy the open road with this fantastic vehicle! It's in good condition and has been clearly well-maintained over the years, offering a smooth, dependable ride that you can truly rely on. While it shows the light, expected signs of careful previous use, it remains a clean and impressive choice for anyone seeking quality and value.",
