    },
    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition. It is mechanically sound and performs reliably, though there are minor signs of cosmetic wear on the interior and exterior. All major systems are functional.",
      "price": 36000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a reliable daily driver. While the engine and transmission are in good working order and the car performs well on the road, it does show its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, some minor dings, and the paint has begun to fade in a few spots. Inside, the upholstery shows visible wear and some staining, and a few of the plastic trim pieces are loose. It is a solid car that gets you from A to B, but it would benefit from some cosmetic TLC and a thorough detailing.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts reliably, making it a solid choice for a daily driver or a long-distance commuter. While the exterior and interior show some minor signs of normal wear and tear, such as small surface scratches and light upholstery aging, the car remains aesthetically pleasing and mechanically sound. All major systems, including the air conditioning and electronics, are fully functional. This is a dependable vehicle for anyone looking for quality and reliability without the premium price of a new or mint-condition car.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. It is operational but shows visible wear on the interior and exterior. Some mechanical components may require maintenance or repair in the near future.",
      "price": 19000.0,
